{"type": "article", "id": 63275, "title": "废弃大理石碎片和树脂的组合，做成家具还不错｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-04-25T22:46:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 10666, "name": "Pentagram"}, {"id": 4877, "name": "百事"}, {"id": 48843, "name": "Talenti"}, {"id": 58151, "name": "Milliong"}, {"id": 57659, "name": "Jiyoun Kim Studio"}, {"id": 58152, "name": "Fict Studio"}, {"id": 58153, "name": "Ludovica + Roberto Palomba"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 126, "image": "img/article/article_show/2019042520022337zBAIT2vKDpb0s5.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Fragment Collection by Fict Studio</h3><p>首尔设计工作室 Fict Studio 推出新品角形家具系列 Fragment，将废弃的大理石碎片与树脂相结合。</p><p>Fragment 系列包括凳子、椅子、边桌和托盘，旨在解决工业大理石废弃物的问题。设计师采用矩形体积的灰色大理石和橙棕色树脂制作家具，可以直角截取，形成几何极简结构。托盘由单一的矩形大理石板和树脂制成，表面带有磨砂处理。</p><p>“韩国不产大理石，所有大理石都是从国外进口的，所以在运输过程中损坏的碎片和剩余的大理石碎片都会失去价值，因为碎片太小而不能使用，所以材料成本很高，” Fict Studio 说。“为了解决这个问题，我们决定重新考虑使用大理石碎片的方式。”设计师希望利用废弃的材料，同时展示“独特的大理石之美”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200257ULS6olEWfgryAjVD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561966\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200258QgOJPnGAr9ktWS1v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.399746\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200258BeCoEUq4NmAfZV6a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714467\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200259v2DuqPiFRXgeoJa7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400169\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200300ESuGsFTgxmwJ6PZK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.399746\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Three Poles Collection by Jiyoun Kim Studio for Milliong</h3><p>Milliong 是韩国一个宠物用品品牌，让与宠物一起度过人生的人的旅行、生活方式变得更有价值和特别。最近，它们与工业设计工作室 Jiyoun Kim Studio 合作，发布了 Three Poles 系列新品。</p><p>整个系列的设计讲述对人类和宠物和谐共享空间的理解，有一种潜在的尊重意识，而不会忽视猫猫的自然习惯。</p><p>Three Poles Cat Tower 外观时尚，结构坚固，采用山毛榉木、胶合板和坚固的金属杆组合设计，可轻松拆卸重新配置，而 Poles Cushion 床则为猫猫提供舒适的休息区。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200330ytnxqwgNfZrLF6vC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.702469\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200330Poieh74GBHtaEjYD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904252003316GMD09eNBlqpOFYn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.716049\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200331jQvA4ia2WZg7ctDX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.656790\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200332Th46Cs1fW5rwp0ab.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.633594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904252003331qk3yxFL0sXjaQvr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200331JPei4z9MRHN5VIr2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.781481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200334wib9ELpmuxg08Rjq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671605\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200334cU0HBj3YLPGs6o4E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.775309\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/78514591/Three-Poles-Cat-Tower-Pet-Living-Design\" rel=\"nofollow\">Behance</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Panama collection by Ludovica + Roberto Palomba for Talenti</h3><p>户外生活设计品牌 Talenti 发布最新家具系列 Panama，操刀设计的是意大利设计师夫妻档 Ludovica + Roberto Palomba。</p><p>Panama 系列试图将用户一秒带入夏天的气氛，灵感来自于在微风中摇曳的棕榈树的阴影。在 Talenti 清新风快的品牌调性智商，绳索、织物木材等不同材质的组合轻松创造出一个休闲区域。</p><p>整个系列包括椅子、躺椅、日光浴床、坐垫和沙发。这些沙发用绳子缠绕在框架上，当阳光穿过它们时会产生错落的光影效果。</p><p>特别是，躺椅的有机轮廓让我们想到了海滩上发现的石头，为这个具有强烈现代感的系列增添了大胆的自然线条。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200419BRGobw9tlX2NmAK8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.313580\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200419XsFlUK6vQiST3RNq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560494\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200420nb08B2leCicq3OXH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.313580\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200421jiNbK7qvn24xRWBZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560494\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200421xRr56v4zJdjkpHw2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560494\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200422cQx5LydVfAB01Fv9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560494\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200419fIRa9zGsDinF5Mhr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560494\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200422hI3KYR1M5gBZtrjL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560494\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200423Ti19SPLtZGn8DJOd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560494\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.talentisrl.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Talenti</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>SodaStream-style drinks dispenser for refillable bottles by PepsiCo</h3><p>最近，百事推出了一款苏打水类饮品的饮料机，可以放在公众场合使用，计划在今年 6 月份尝试在大学、企业和酒店投放。它可以提供 6 种风味的无糖苏打水，用户可以自定义苏打水的二氧化碳含量、温度和口味浓度，比如草莓、柠檬薄荷和橙子的浓度。</p><p>值得一提的是，这款苏打水饮料机会显示每次使用时节省的塑料瓶的数量。这也是百事“超越瓶子”（Beyond Water）计划的一部分，目标是减少塑料瓶的使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200506AYcN1m4WyObjXkGu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904252005077lxQdHGB1ZpfINwA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200508Lr5NiVDPhuoMf6Gt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200509rMew19uQN2kKaciy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200510wVMyNP8ldTkbpqjr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.266074\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2019/04/25/pepsico-drink-dispenser-refillable-bottles/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Flight Center Gothic by Pentagram</h3><p>2015 年，纽约州长宣布以 TWA 酒店的形式复活尼迪机场的 TWA 航天中心。最近，进行大规模烦心设计后的酒店终于要开放了。平面设计公司 Pentagram 被邀请为 TWA 酒店创建新字体。</p><p>这种名为 Flight Center Gothic 的新字体是基于美国建筑师 Saarinen 在 1962 年开业时为机场做建筑设计的思路。字体设计意在体现飞行运动的感觉，弯曲细节也参考了建筑中的未来主义建筑元素，如翼形外部。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200548IuRawQq3rOMF96YB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.691624\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904252005473DhTjfeCOxoMG04H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200548Kz51efr3pv4QxLZJ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904252005489pgEVSIB2PjThYOl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714467\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190425200553Bm20b9uXlKsQ7FAH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.077834\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}